Moss (Mace of the shadowed souls, city of mist) 1hb, Ebon Mace 1hb (Sebilis), Noctivagant Blade 1hs (Karnors), Jade Mace 1hb (Karnors). You'll need 1-2 50+ Groups for CoM if you don't know the place, 1 Group for Karnors but the Hands/Warlord Room is permacamped. BE Armor from karnors, Plane Armor at 46+. Clay Guardian Shield, Sarnak Battle Shield.<br>
