<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Our Ranger is currently in Ivy, using the Blackened Alloy bastard sword we got in Runnyeye EONS ago, but is still a very good and fast, although 2-handed, weapon. We are trying to get her to start using two 1handed weapons, but she is married to that sword, it seems; some suggestions for something attainable by us that might light her fire would be appreciated.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
